OL,3,CGrinding insects into flour 'could
OL,4,Cmake protein source more appealing'
OL,6,FIncorporating flour made from insects
OL,7,Finto processed foods could help people
OL,8,Fin the UK overcome their reluctance to
OL,9,Feat them - and help tackle obesity.
OL,11,FInsects are protein-rich, easier to
OL,12,Ffarm, lower in fat and have less of an
OL,13,Fimpact on the environment than
OL,14,Flivestock, according to researchers.
OL,16,FHowever, a survey conducted by
OL,17,Facademics found the majority of people
OL,18,Fwould be unwilling to eat insects.
OL,20,FThe online poll of 603 UK adults was
OL,21,Fcarried out between 2019 and 2020.
