OL,4,Cmake protein source more appealing'
OL,6,FPeople were asked questions about
OL,7,Ftheir age, gender, ethnicity and
OL,8,Feducation level, as well as their
OL,9,Flevel of concern about the environment.
OL,11,FThey were also asked to complete a
OL,12,F"food disgust scale", which rated
OL,13,Ftheir disgust at less commonly eaten
OL,14,Fparts of animals, such as offal, as
OL,15,Fwell as mouldy food.
OL,17,FThe poll also included questions on
OL,18,Fhow they would perceive insects to
OL,19,Ftaste or feel.
