OL,6,F"This has been done successfully with
OL,7,Frice products fortified with cricket
OL,8,For locust flours in other parts of the
OL,9,Fworld."
OL,11,FLead author Dr Lauren McGale, of ,
OL,12,Fadded: "Insects are a potentially rich
OL,13,Fsource of protein and micro-nutrients
OL,14,Fand could help provide a solution to
OL,15,Fthe double burden of obesity and
OL,16,Fundernutrition.
