OL,3,CGrinding insects into flour 'could
OL,4,Cmake protein source more appealing'
OL,6,F"Some insect proteins, such as ground
OL,7,Fcrickets or freeze-dried mealworms,
OL,8,Fare cheaper and easier to farm, often
OL,9,Flower in fat and have a lower
OL,10,Fenvironmental impact than traditional
OL,11,Flivestock."
OL,13,FDr Sharps said: "But if insects are to
OL,14,Fbe a mainstream part of the Western
OL,15,Fdiet, the disgust factor is one of
OL,16,Fmost important challenges to be
OL,17,Fovercome.
OL,19,F"Afterall, there may be eventually no
OL,20,Fchoice with climate change and
OL,21,Fprojected global population growth."
